OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FScott Mills to replace     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FSteve Wright on BBC Radio 2
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fafternoon show             
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, BBC Radio 2 DJ Steve Wright has        
OL,6, announced his weekday afternoon show is
OL,7, to end after more than 20 years.       
OL,9,FWright said Radio 2's boss had told him
OL,10,Fshe wanted to do "something different" 
OL,11,Fwith his mid-afternoon slot.           
OL,13,FHe will be replaced by Scott Mills, who
OL,14,Fcurrently hosts afternoons on Radio 1, 
OL,15,Fin a shake-up of the daytime schedule. 
OL,17,FThe new afternoon show, hosted by      
OL,18,FMills, will be cut by an hour, while   
OL,19,FSara Cox's drivetime show will be      
OL,20,Fextended by an hour and start at 16:00.
